 ">full entry</a></span></span></span></div><div class="collapse" htag="div" hclass="collapse"><span class="unbox" unbox="wordorigin" id="adverb_unbox_1"><span class="box_title">Word Origin</span><span class="body"><span class="p">late Middle English: from Latin <span class="ei">adverbium</span>, from <span class="ei">ad-</span> ‘to’ (expressing addition) + <span class="ei">verbum</span> ‘word, verb’.</span></span></span></div>    <div id="ring-links-box">
